EFF leader Julius Malema has welcomed his third son. Malema announced the birth of his son on his Instagram on Wednesday, captioning a picture of his wife Mantoa, he said: “Bana ba mberengwa, tšhipi ya bokgalaka, congratulations mmago bašimane. It’s a boy, his name is Kopano.” Malema’s eldest son is from his previous relationship and he welcomed his second son in October 2016. -TNA Reporter